145
00:11:08,647 --> 00:11:10,747
Mr. Honjou, everyone,

146
00:11:10,747 --> 00:11:12,347
thank you so much.

147
00:11:12,347 --> 00:11:14,647
That over there is Mr. Hirose,

148
00:11:14,647 --> 00:11:16,647
