00:19:17,147 --> 00:19:20,347
Is this the famous "Sleeping Kogorou"?

274
00:19:22,247 --> 00:19:23,747
That is the famous...

275
00:19:23,747 --> 00:19:27,647
Mr. Honjou, it seems like you have fallen into a trap.

276
00:19:27,647 --> 00:19:29,947
-A trap? -Yes.

277
00:19:29,947 --> 00:19:32,647
Someone in this party who is jealous of you

278
00:19:32,647 --> 00:19:35,247
must have come to this party to embarrass you.

279
00:19:35,247 --> 00:19:38,147
They sneaked into your wine cellar

280
00:19:38,147 --> 00:19:40,947
to ruin the wine you have just served.

281
00:19:40,947 --> 00:19:44,347
That's right. That must be it.

282
00:19:45,647 --> 00:19:47,247
Who did it?

283
00:19:48,347 --> 00:19:50,347
But that's impossible.

284
00:19:50,347 --> 00:19:52,547
In order to get into the wine storeroom,

285
00:19:52,547 --> 00:19:55,047
they would have to use my fingerprints to unlock the system.

286
00:19:55,047 --> 00:19:56,747
Most likely the culprit

287
00:19:56,747 --> 00:20:00,347
is someone who's familiar with the security system.

288
00:20:00,347 --> 00:20:04,547
And it's possible they might still be hiding in there,

289
00:20:04,547 --> 00:20:07,347
which is where the remaining wine is.

290
00:20:07,347 --> 00:20:09,147
That would be horrible.

291
00:20:09,147 --> 00:20:12,447
We have to stop that from happening.

292
00:20:12,447 --> 00:20:14,447
Let's go to the cellar now.

293
00:20:14,447 --> 00:20:16,747
Oh no. I can go alone.

294
00:20:16,747 --> 00:20:18,047
It's dangerous.

295
00:20:18,047 --> 00:20:21,147
We don't know what this culprit is capable of.

296
00:20:21,147 --> 00:20:22,847
And we do not want to lose any more wine

297
00:20:22,847 --> 00:20:26,147
while we try to get them.

298
00:20:26,147 --> 00:20:27,147
But...

299
00:20:27,147 --> 00:20:29,147
-I will go too. -Me too.

300
00:20:29,147 --> 00:20:32,047
-We should hurry. -Where is the wine cellar?

301
00:20:38,047 --> 00:20:40,147
Mr. Akamaru. Mr. Akamaru.

302
00:20:40,147 --> 00:20:41,847
Can you hear me?

303
00:20:41,847 --> 00:20:42,847
Mr. Akamaru.

304
00:20:44,547 --> 00:20:46,247
Call the ambulance.

305
00:20:46,247 --> 00:20:47,647
Yes. Right away.

306
00:20:49,847 --> 00:20:53,347
What is all this, Mr. Honjou?

307
00:20:53,347 --> 00:20:55,747
I... I...

308
00:20:55,747 --> 00:20:58,847
Mr. Honjou, I will notify the police.

309
00:21:04,347 --> 00:21:07,147
He always mocked me.

310
00:21:07,147 --> 00:21:10,547
Said that I have no class or education

311
00:21:10,547 --> 00:21:14,447
to present myself as a wine lover.

312
00:21:14,447 --> 00:21:19,247
Mr. Honjou, do you really love wine?

313
00:21:19,247 --> 00:21:20,847
Yes, I do.

314
00:21:20,847 --> 00:21:23,247
Well, I don't think so.

315
00:21:23,247 --> 00:21:27,847
The wine cellar is a sacred place for the wine lover.

316
00:21:27,847 --> 00:21:30,647
And to use that to cover up a crime

317
00:21:30,647 --> 00:21:31,647
is unforgivable.

318
00:21:37,147 --> 00:21:40,347
Luckily, Mr. Akamaru was stabilized.

319
00:21:40,347 --> 00:21:43,347
And the case was closed.

320
00:21:43,347 --> 00:21:47,547
Perhaps the true victim in this case might be

321
00:21:47,547 --> 00:21:50,247
the bottle whose taste was ruined when it got involved

322
00:21:50,247 --> 00:21:52,447
in the dirty infighting between humans...

323
00:21:52,447 --> 00:21:54,847
That bottle of wine.

324
00:23:20,347 --> 00:23:22,847
"Mouri Detective Agency" -The sweetness, the soft flavor.

325
00:23:22,847 --> 00:23:25,547
Vintage wine does make the difference.

326
00:23:28,147 --> 00:23:29,747
How much was that wine?

327
00:23:29,747 --> 00:23:31,047
It was 10,000 yen,

328
00:23:31,047 --> 00:23:36,247
but I had the people at the store switch it to a 1000 yen bottle.

329
00:23:43,247 --> 00:23:44,947
"Tres Bien"

330
00:23:45,947 --> 00:23:49,647
It's lucky for us that you can't recognize the taste.

331
00:23:51,620 --> 00:23:53,420
Next Conan's Hint:

332
00:23:53,760 --> 00:23:56,160
"Shinichi Kudo".

